This animation trailer was built with HTML5 WebGL and run in browser.

To run it, first you need to make sure your browser supports WebGL, you may check it at get.webgl.org

run with FireFox: you can just drop the studio6_trailer.html into browser

run with Chrome: due to Chrome is very restrited in loading files from local driver, you need to move the whole folder to under a web server, such as ~/Sites/ if you use a Mac and check the 'Web Sharing' in 'System Preferences' -> 'Sharing';  then you can load the file in browser as http://localhost/~yourusernameInMac/HTML5-WebGL-trailer/mu_studio_trailer.html

